sentences: Jiří Kabeš, alias Kába (* 26 March 1946 in Křemín, Czechoslovakia) is a Czech rock singer, violist, violinist, guitarist and songwriter.

sentences: He was a longtime member of The Plastic People of the Universe where he played on viola and violin, occasionally sang and played on theremin.

sentences: In the early seventies he played with rock'n'roll group The Old Teenagers.
